text: Nick Lowe (born 1949), is an English singer-songwriter, musician and producer. Nick Lowe may also refer to: *Nick Lowe (classicist) (born 1956), British classical scholar and film critic *Nick Lowe (comics) (born 1979), American comics editor ==See also== *Nicholas Low (1739–1826), American merchant and developer
title: Nick Lowe (disambiguation)
